((SELECT id FROM programs WHERE slug = 'naan-mudhalvan-6th-sem-2025'), 'about', 'About the Program', ' Rareminds delivered a specialized 45-hour experiential training program during the 6th Semester of the 2024–2025 academic year. These mandatory programs provided immersive, hands-on learning experiences in the following sector : EV Battery Management System. The program combined in-person sessions with LMS-enabled learning, allowing students to work on simulations, projects, and practical applications from the outset.'),
